#QC on housekeeping genes
qc_hkg(hkg)

Take geometric average all housekeeping genes

mean_hkg <- calculate_mean_hkg(hkg)

Remove outliers

mean_hkg$CT_avg_hkg <- remove_outliers(mean_hkg$CT_avg_hkg)
